---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHero from "../components/PageHero.astro";

// Refund / cancellation policy for card purchases.
// NOTE: adjust the cancellation windows and amounts to your final commercial terms.
const updated = "21 July 2026";
---

<BaseLayout
  current="pricing"
  title="Refund Policy — Coworking Prilep"
  description="How refunds and cancellations work for memberships, passes, credits, and room bookings paid by card at Coworking Prilep."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Legal"
    title="Refund Policy"
    subtitle="How cancellations and refunds work for memberships, passes, credits, and room bookings paid by card."
  />

  <article class="px-6 pb-24 md:px-12 md:pb-32">
    <div class="prose-cws mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <p class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.25em] text-bone/40 uppercase">
        Last updated: {updated}
      </p>

      <h2>1. Scope</h2>
      <p>
        This policy applies to purchases made from Coworking Prilep, operated by
        <strong>Dastian DOO Prilep</strong>, whether paid on our website by card
        or in person. It covers memberships, day and hour passes, hour credits, and
        meeting-room and classroom bookings.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Your right to cancel a distance purchase</h2>
      <p>
        Under the Law on Consumer Protection of North Macedonia, for services
        bought at a distance you generally have <strong>14 days</strong> to
        withdraw. Where you ask us to begin the service before the 14 days end
        (for example, an immediately active membership or a booking for a date
        within that period), you agree that the withdrawal right ends once the
        service has been fully performed, and that for partially used services we
        may charge for the part already provided.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Memberships</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Monthly memberships renew each month. You can cancel at any time; the
          cancellation takes effect at the end of the current paid month and you
          keep access until then.
        </li>
        <li>
          We do not refund the unused part of a month once the month has started,
          unless required by law or agreed by us in writing.
        </li>
        <li>
          If you cancel before your membership has started and before any access
          has been used, we refund it in full.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Passes &amp; hour credits</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Unused passes and credits are refundable within 14 days of purchase, provided none of the hours or access have been used.</li>
        <li>Once any part of a pass or credit has been used, it is non-refundable, and unused hours simply expire at the end of their validity period.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Meeting room &amp; classroom bookings</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Cancelled 24+ hours before</strong> the booking start time: full refund.</li>
        <li><strong>Cancelled less than 24 hours before</strong>, or a no-show: non-refundable.</li>
        <li>If we cancel a confirmed booking for any reason, you receive a full refund or a free re-booking, your choice.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>6. Incorrect, duplicate, or unauthorised charges</h2>
      <p>
        If you are charged in error, charged twice, or believe a charge was not
        authorised, contact us right away. Verified incorrect or duplicate charges
        are refunded in full.
      </p>

      <h2>7. How refunds are paid</h2>
      <p>
        Approved refunds are returned to the <strong>same card</strong> used for
        the original payment, through the bank's payment gateway. We process
        approved refunds within a <strong>maximum of 14 days</strong>; it may then
        take a further few business days for your bank to show the amount,
        depending on your card issuer. Refunds are made in the original currency
        (MKD).
      </p>

      <h2>8. How to request a refund</h2>
      <p>
        Email <a href="mailto:coworkingprilep@outlook.com">coworkingprilep@outlook.com</a>
        with your name, the email used for the purchase, the transaction date and
        amount, and the reason for the request. We aim to respond within
        <strong>5 business days</strong>.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Dastian DOO Prilep, Kej 1-vi Maj no. 9, Prilep, North Macedonia ·
        <a href="mailto:coworkingprilep@outlook.com">coworkingprilep@outlook.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
